snippet.title: Rusk, TX Amber Alert on KNCT 91.3FM | EAS #1258
snippet.description:
305 WOUS44 KEWX 311109 CAEEWX TXC013-019-021-029-031-053-055-091-123-127-137-149-163-171-177- 187-209-255-259-265-271-285-287-299-323-325-385-453-463-465-491- 493-507-311215- BULLETIN - EAS ACTIVATION REQUESTED CHILD ABDUCTION EMERGENCY 

TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY 

RELAYED BY NATIONAL WEATHER SERVICE AUSTIN/SAN ANTONIO TX 609 AM CDT TUE AUG 31 2021

 THE FOLLOWING MESSAGE IS TRANSMITTED AT THE REQUEST OF THE TEXAS DEPARTMENT OF PUBLIC SAFETY. THIS IS A CHILD ABDUCTION ALERT ISSUED BY THE TEXAS AMBER ALERT NETWORK THE CHEROKEE COUNTY SHERIFFS OFFICE IS SEARCHING FOR ASHLYNN WELLS, WHITE, FEMALE, 10 YEARS OLD, DATE OF BIRTH FEBRUARY FIRST...2011, HEIGHT 5 FOOT 2 INCHES, WEIGHT 109 POUNDS, BLONDE HAIR, BLUE EYES, AND LAST SEEN WEARING PEACH T-SHIRT, PEACH SHORTS, GRAY AND PINK NIKE SHOES. ASHLYNN HAS DIMPLES, A SCAR ON HER RIGHT RING FINGER, AND A BLACK BIRTHMARK ON HER LEFT THIGH. THE CHEROKEE COUNTY SHERIFFS OFFICE IS SEARCHING FOR DESMOND WELLS THE THIRD, WHITE, MALE, 11 YEARS OLD, DATE OF BIRTH SEPTEMBER TWENTY FIFTH 2009, HEIGHT 5 FOOT 5 INCHES, WEIGHT 154 POUNDS, BLONDE HAIR, BROWN EYES, AND LAST SEEN WEARING BLUE AND LACK T-SHIRT, GRAY SHORTS, WOLVERINE HIKING BOOTS. HE HAS A SCAR ON HIS LEFT SHIN. POLICE ARE LOOKING FOR JESSE RAY SCHMIDT, WHITE, MALE, 32 YEARS OLD, DATE OF BIRTH MAY FIFTEENTH 1989, HEIGHT 5 FOOT 10 INCHES, WEIGHT 160 POUNDS, BROWN HAIR, HAZEL EYES, IN CONNECTION WITH THEIR ABDUCTION. THE SUSPECT IS DRIVING A BLACK, 2012 HONDA CIVIC WITH A TEXAS, LICENSE PLATE NUMBER OF B-N-X-6-1-5-5. THE SUSPECT WAS LAST HEARD FROM IN RUSK, TEXAS. LAW ENFORCEMENT OFFICIALS BELIEVE THESE CHILDREN TO BE IN GRAVE OR IMMEDIATE DANGER. IF YOU HAVE ANY INFORMATION REGARDING THIS ABDUCTION, CALL THE CHEROKEE COUNTY SHERIFFS OFFICE AT 9 0 3 - 6 8 3 - 2 2 7 1. NEWS MEDIA POINT OF CONTACT IS CHEROKEE COUNTY SHERIFFS OFFICE AT 9 0 3 - 6 8 3 - 2 2 7 1. $$
